value_proposition_en:
[Automatic translation follows] The French Center for Funds and Foundations aims to promote knowledge of the fund and foundation sector

The French Center for Funds and Foundations aims to bring together all endowment funds and foundations. Its mission is to help to get to know the sector, to promote its development and to represent its common interests for the benefit of the general interest.

It contributes to the expression, representation and promotion of a philanthropic, dynamic, innovative and recognized sector, committed to serving causes of general interest.

 Bring together Funds and Foundations in all their diversity;

Create a link between all those who develop and animate a foundation or an endowment fund;

Promote and develop the philanthropic initiative;

Spokesperson for funds and foundations in France with public authorities and the voice of French funds and foundations in Europe and around the world;

Provide funds and foundations with a single resource and training centre.

The French Center for Funds and Foundations conducts all of its actions in a spirit of openness, innovation, transparency and integrity, at the service of all, while respecting its social utility.

The French Center for Funds and Foundations believes in the benefits of exchange and collaborative actions;
promotes the diversity of funds and foundations regardless of their statutes, their founders, their missions and their operating methods.

